---
title: Duck Banh Mi with Quick-Pickled Veggies and Cilantro Mayo
description: Rich duck breast adds a touch of luxury to this Vietnamese street food favourite! Quick-pickled veggies add balance to tender duck and cilantro mayo.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/banh-mi-au-canard-576b119e.jpg
